ng h ca mnh qua cc bc sau:</p><p><strong>Bc 1</strong>: Truy cp ng dng Garmin Connect trn in thoi v kt ni vi ng h Garmin.</p><p><strong>Bc 2</strong>: Chn Thm  pha di gc phi mn hnh in thoi v chn Ca hng Connect IQ.</p><p><strong>Bc 3</strong>: Xut hin giao din chnh ca Connect IQ, chn mt ng h yu thch v ti xung. Sau&nbsp;&nbsp;mt ng h&nbsp;va ti s c trn thit b&nbsp;Garmin&nbsp;ca bn.</p><p><strong>Bc 4</strong>:&nbsp;&nbsp;nt UP =&gt; MT NG H =&gt; UP/ DOWN, chn n mt ng h va ti v nhn p dng.</p><h3><strong>Pin dng 13 ngy, 48 ngy khi&nbsp; ch&nbsp; tit kim</strong></h3><p>Trang b vin pin cho thi gian s dng ln n&nbsp;13 ngy trong mt ln sc, dng c 36 gi khi bt&nbsp;GPS, dng c 48 ngy khi bt ch  tit kim pin. Ngoi ra cn c tnh nng Power Mode, gip ngui dng c th xem c nhng tnh nng tn&nbsp;pin, qua  c th tt tnh nng , ko di tui th pin.</p><h3><strong>Theo di sc kho v tim mch lin tc</strong></h3><p>Trang b cc n cm bin o nhp tim quang hc  mt lng v dy eo m st c tay gip kh nng&nbsp;o nhp tim,&nbsp;theo di gic ng,&nbsp;tnh trng stress c hiu qu, chnh xc, a ra nhng d liu v cnh bo khi&nbsp;thy tim hay gic ng ngi dng&nbsp;c du hiu bt thng.</p><h3><strong>Theo di sc kho&nbsp;ngi eo mi&nbsp;ngy</strong></h3><p>H tr a GNSS (GPS, GLONASS v Galileo)  H thng v tinh ton cu gip&nbsp;theo di kh nng di chuyn k c khi ngi eo  nhng ni kh nh v GPS. Vi tnh nng cnh bo an ton, khi bn cm thy nguy him&nbsp;hoc ng h cm thy bn ang gp s c chn thng hay t ng, Garmin Fenix 6 s gi v tr ca bn n nhng&nbsp;lin h khn cp m bn&nbsp; lu trc&nbsp;.</p><h3><strong>Luyn tp th thao hiu qu v&nbsp;th v hn</strong></h3><p>Garmin Fenix 6 tch hp nhiu ng dng th thao&nbsp;nh bi li, ln, chy b, xe p, i b ng di, cho thuyn, chy b a hnh, trt tuyt  khu ngh dng v khu vng v, chi golf, leo ni v cc mn khc. Tnh nng PacePro hng dn ngi dng chy theo tc  ph hp theo mc tiu&nbsp; ra&nbsp;trong sut qu trnh tp, ngoi ra&nbsp;c th truy cp Connect IQ  c th ti thm cc&nbsp;bi tp th thao&nbsp;khc.</p><h3><strong>iu khin pht nhc t xa</strong></h3><p>Garmin Fe